2017年1月18日，連續四次的主地震襲擊[[意大利|意大利]]中部[[阿布魯佐|阿布魯佐]]、[[拉齊奧|拉齊奧]]、[[馬爾凱|馬爾凱]]及[[翁布里亞|翁布里亞]]地區<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.repubblica.it/cronaca/2017/01/18/news/scossa_di_terremoto_avvertita_anche_a_roma-156285725/?ref=HREA-1|title=Terremoto, 4 scosse sopra magnitudo 5: torna la paura nel Centro Italia in ginocchio per la neve|date=18 January 2017|publisher=|accessdate=18 January 2017|archive-date=2017-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171023161854/http://www.repubblica.it/cronaca/2017/01/18/news/scossa_di_terremoto_avvertita_anche_a_roma-156285725/?ref=HREA-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在同一時間，該地區受一個強烈[[2017年1月歐洲寒潮|寒潮]]影響<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.repubblica.it/cronaca/2017/01/17/news/maltempo_neve_abbatte_cavo_in_autostrada_chiusa_a14_in_abruzzo-156195499/|title=Maltempo, Abruzzo: senza luce un quarto della popolazione. Governo manda l'Esercito|date=17 January 2017|publisher=|accessdate=18 January 2017|archive-date=2017-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170119120810/http://www.repubblica.it/cronaca/2017/01/17/news/maltempo_neve_abbatte_cavo_in_autostrada_chiusa_a14_in_abruzzo-156195499/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 地震 == 
當地時間1月18日上午10時25分，一個5.3級地震襲擊[[拉奎拉|拉奎拉]]以北25公里，震源深度9公里<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.emsc-csem.org/Earthquake/earthquake.php?id=560763|title=Earthquake, Magnitude 5.3 - CENTRAL ITALY - 2017 January 18, 09:25:40 UTC|publisher=|accessdate=18 January 2017|archive-date=2018-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180625161714/https://www.emsc-csem.org/Earthquake/earthquake.php?id=560763|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

當地時間11時14分，同一震央發出一個更強的5.7級震盪<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.emsc-csem.org/Earthquake/earthquake.php?id=560781|title=Earthquake, Magnitude 5.7 - CENTRAL ITALY - 2017 January 18, 10:14:10 UTC|publisher=|accessdate=18 January 2017|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912114907/https://www.emsc-csem.org/Earthquake/earthquake.php?id=560781|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第三個初步強度為5.6級的地震在11分後發生<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.emsc-csem.org/Earthquake/earthquake.php?id=560787|title=Earthquake, Magnitude 5.6 - CENTRAL ITALY - 2017 January 18, 10:25:25 UTC|publisher=|accessdate=18 January 2017|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912114854/https://www.emsc-csem.org/Earthquake/earthquake.php?id=560787|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在當地時間下午2時33分，發生第四個地震，強度為5.2級<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.emsc-csem.org/Earthquake/earthquake.php?id=560908|title=Earthquake, Magnitude 5.2 - CENTRAL ITALY - 2017 January 18, 13:33:37 UTC|publisher=|accessdate=18 January 2017|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912114855/https://www.emsc-csem.org/Earthquake/earthquake.php?id=560908|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這些地震隨後發生多個剩震。

地震在意大利中部其他城市有強烈震感，包括[[羅馬|羅馬]]。地鐵及多間學校也進行撤離<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2017/01/18/europe/italy-earthquake-rome-amatrice/index.html|title=Rome's subway evacuated as quakes rock Italy|last=CNN|first=Angela Dewan and Barbie Nadeau|website=CNN|access-date=2017-01-19|archive-date=2017-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118233216/http://www.cnn.com/2017/01/18/europe/italy-earthquake-rome-amatrice/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最強的震波在克羅地亞的沿海地區也有震感（[[麥加利地震烈度|烈度]]為三級）<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gfz.hr/seizmologija/izvjestaj.php?id=461|title=Geofizički odsjek PMF-a|website=www.gfz.hr|access-date=2017-01-19|archive-date=2017-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170119051724/http://www.gfz.hr/seizmologija/izvjestaj.php?id=461|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

===雪崩===
[[File:Rigopiano_Hotel.jpg|thumb]]
1月18日晚上，被認為是地震觸發的一場雪崩掩埋了位於[[阿布魯佐|阿布魯佐]]山區的Rigopiano酒店，造成多人死亡<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lastampa.it/2017/01/19/italia/cronache/hotel-sommerso-da-una-valanga-postterremoto-soccorritori-al-lavoro-persone-in-salvo-ePTkV1IcRx1t8fYScytnOM/pagina.html |title=-{Hotel sommerso da una valanga dopo il sisma. “Tanti morti, estratto il primo corpo”}- |accessdate=2017-01-19 |archive-date=2017-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170120001757/http://www.lastampa.it/2017/01/19/italia/cronache/hotel-sommerso-da-una-valanga-postterremoto-soccorritori-al-lavoro-persone-in-salvo-ePTkV1IcRx1t8fYScytnOM/pagina.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-38674788 | title = 'Many dead' in avalanche on Italy hotel in the Abruzzo | publisher = BBC News | date = 19 January 2017 | accessdate = 19 January 2017 | archive-date = 2017-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170119133046/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-38674788 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。當時酒店內共有40人，包括28名旅客及12名員工<ref name="Xinhua - 24-01-17">{{cite web|title=Death toll of Italy hotel avalanche keeps rising, as first funerals held|url=http://www.globaltimes.cn/content/1030590.shtml|website=Global Times|publisher=Xinhua|accessdate=25 January 2017|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202024705/http://www.globaltimes.cn/content/1030590.shtml|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。地震發生短時間後當地報導，雪崩來襲時旅客聚集在酒店一樓並等待疏散<ref name="AFP" />。衝擊導致酒店的部份樓頂倒塌，並且往山下移動了10米（33尺）<ref name="BBC News">{{cite web|title=Rigopiano hotel avalanche: Italian rescuers find no sign of life|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-38674788|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=19 January 2017|archive-date=2017-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170127124642/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-38674788|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

已證實29人在雪崩中衰生<ref name="TASS Russian News Agency">{{cite web|title=Italy’s Rigopiano hotel death toll reaches 29, rescue operation over|url=http://tass.com/society/927387|website=TASS Russian News Agency|accessdate=26 January 2017}}{{Dead link|date=2019年9月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。共有9人獲救<ref name="Reuters">{{cite web|last1=Denti|first1=Antonio|title=More survivors in Italian avalanche hotel as death toll rises to five|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-italy-quake-avalanche-idUSKBN155070?il=0|agency=Reuters|accessdate=21 January 2017|archive-date=2017-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170124161243/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-italy-quake-avalanche-idUSKBN155070?il=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.repubblica.it/cronaca/2017/01/20/news/valanga_rigopiano_farindola_gran_sasso_soccorsi_ricerche-156436519/?ref=HREA-1|title=Miracolo Rigopiano: 10 ancora vivi, salvati 4 bambini|date=20 January 2017|accessdate=2017-01-26|archive-date=2017-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170126162638/http://www.repubblica.it/cronaca/2017/01/20/news/valanga_rigopiano_farindola_gran_sasso_soccorsi_ricerche-156436519/?ref=HREA-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>，另外2人因雪崩來襲時站在酒店外面而生還<ref name="The Guardian">{{cite web|last1=Giuffrida|first1=Angela|title=Italy avalanche: many feared dead as Rigopiano hotel engulfed|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/jan/19/italy-earthquakes-avalanche-hotel|website=The Guardian|accessdate=19 January 2017|archive-date=2017-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170126075415/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/jan/19/italy-earthquakes-avalanche-hotel|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AFP">{{cite web|title=Killer avalanche turns Italian hotel into 'coffin'|url=https://www.afp.com/en/news/23/killer-avalanche-turns-italian-hotel-coffin|agency=Agence France-Presse|accessdate=19 January 2017|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170119191438/https://www.afp.com/en/news/23/killer-avalanche-turns-italian-hotel-coffin|archivedate=2017年1月19日}}</ref>。獲救的十一人中有十人受到因[[失溫症|失溫症]]產生的輕傷<ref name="The Guardian"/><ref name="FOX 40 – CNN Wire">{{cite web|title='Angels! Angels!' Avalanche Survivors Call Out to Rescuers|url=http://fox40.com/2017/01/20/italy-avalanche-6-people-found-alive-in-buried-hotel-2-rescued/|website=FOX 40|publisher=CNN|accessdate=21 January 2017|archive-date=2017-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170126095531/http://fox40.com/2017/01/20/italy-avalanche-6-people-found-alive-in-buried-hotel-2-rescued/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第十一人的上臂压傷並需要進行手術<ref name="Fox News World">{{cite web|title=4 more survivors pulled out of Italy's avalanche-hit hotel|url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2017/01/21/4-more-survivors-pulled-out-italys-avalanche-hit-hotel.html|website=Fox News World|accessdate=22 January 2017|archive-date=2017-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170125031319/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2017/01/21/4-more-survivors-pulled-out-italys-avalanche-hit-hotel.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在1月23日，拯救人員發現第7件屍體，但也在堆雪下找到3隻生還的小狗，意味著失蹤的22人或可能生還<ref>{{cite web|title=Italian avalanche: hope for survivors after three puppies found alive in rubble|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/jan/23/italian-avalanche-three-puppies-found-alive-in-hotel-rubble|work=The Guardian|date=23 January 2017|accessdate=24 January 2017|archive-date=2017-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170126075403/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/jan/23/italian-avalanche-three-puppies-found-alive-in-hotel-rubble|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但是後來顯示已沒有其他人在雪崩下生還<ref name="TASS Russian News Agency"/>。

== 地質情況 == 

地震發生在一個位於[[2016年意大利中部地震|2016年意大利中部地震]]、{{le|2016年10月意大利中部地震|October 2016 Central Italy earthquakes}}及在{{le|1997年翁布里亞和馬爾凱地震|1997 Umbria and Marche earthquake}}之間的{{le|地震空白帶|seismic gap}}。在2016年之前，該間隙在過去100年也沒有發生地震<ref>since there is that 1879 quake in the map, not more offside than the actual quake its safer to say so, instead telling the 157 years from source spiegel.de</ref> 。

四次同樣是5級以上的突發震蕩在3小時內快速發生，意大利[[國立地球物理與火山學研究所|國家地球物理和火山學研究所]]的地震學家稱之為「一種近代歷史上的新現象」<ref>{{cite news|title=Ingv, quattro terremoti in tre ore, mai vista una serie simile - Terra e Poli - Scienza&Tecnica|url=https://www.ansa.it/scienza/notizie/rubriche/terrapoli/2017/01/18/terremoto-di-magnitudo-53-vicino-laquila_279f2d64-c019-4380-bb33-897eb04393ce.html|work=ANSA.it|agency=ANSA|date=18 January 2017|language=it|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2017-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118220618/http://www.ansa.it/scienza/notizie/rubriche/terrapoli/2017/01/18/terremoto-di-magnitudo-53-vicino-laquila_279f2d64-c019-4380-bb33-897eb04393ce.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並把它與{{le|1980年伊爾皮尼亞地震|1980 Irpinia earthquake}}相提並論，後者在80秒發生三次不同的地震。

在[[亞平寧山脈|亞平寧山脈]]斷層活動過程是相對較新的一個地質術語，根據[[斯坦福大學|斯坦福大學]]的地震學家{{le|Ross Stein|Ross Stein}}稱，自從500,000年前斷層變得更加不規則，所以前震會引發更多震蕩{{Citation needed|date=January 2017}}。

